          <div class="flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="flow-step"><span class="fnum">02</span>Reconnaissance &amp; lateral movement across network</div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="flow-step"><span class="fnum">03</span>Data exfiltration (for double extortion leverage)</div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="flow-step"><span class="fnum">04</span>Mass encryption of files across all systems</div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="flow-step"><span class="fnum">05</span>Ransom demand in Bitcoin or Monero</div>
        </div>
      </div>
